snippet.title: First Official Nova Alpha Video
snippet.description:
Hello everyone!

The official Nova Open Alpha starts today. This currently includes 5 Elemental Souls: Fire, Frost, Shadow, Nature, and Storm, and 2 (soon-to-be 3) developed zones: The Forest, The Dungeon, and the Desert, all of which are featured in this video. 

Follow for more content weekly!

Find us at PAX East 2022 April 21-24
Join our Discord to play: https://discord.gg/8N8KQVUhR4
Find us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nova.game.official/
